headline: Conagra Brands (CAG): Assessing Valuation Following Slim Jim and Buffalo Wild Wings New Product Collaboration
summary: Conagra Brands (CAG) just rolled out something many snack fans and investors might not have seen coming: a collaboration that brings together its Slim Jim brand and Buffalo Wild Wings for two new chicken stick flavors. This partnership arrives at a time when the chicken stick segment is seeing strong momentum, with 84% growth over the past three years. For investors, a move like this signals more than just trendy flavors; it points to Conagra Brands’ efforts to harness category growth and...
